      <bioghist id="aspace_4c416e584ea3461cb4051976c8eae927">
         <head>Emlen Etting (1905-1993)</head>
         <p>Emlen Etting, American poet, painter, sculptor, illustrator, and filmmaker.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_13fdff1d04f13c3c38ec91fdad17450c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Emlen Etting Papers contain correspondence, writings, printed material, artwork, and photographs that document the professional and personal life of visual artist Emlen Etting. The papers span the years 1924 to 1982.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_a700f46194152ffe316c430911156c87">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into three series: I. Writings, 1924-1957. II.Correspondence, 1927-1976. III. Other Papers, 1940-1982.</p>  
      </arrangement>
